Package io.spine.code.gen.java

This package contains tools for generating Java code as well as working with already generated code.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GeneratedMethodSpec
    A JavaPoet-based spec of a generated method.
    GeneratedTypeSpec
    A JavaPoet-based spec of a generated type.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Annotations
    A factory for Java annotation specs.
    ColumnFactory
    Generates an entity column enumeration for the given message type.
    EmptyPrivateCtor
    A spec of a private parameter-less constructor.
    FieldFactory
    Generates a field enumeration for the given message type.
    FieldName
    A name of a field declared in a Java class.
    GeneratedBySpine
    Provides fields for Generated annotation used by code generation tools for marking source code generated by Spine Model Compiler.
    GeneratedJavadoc
    A JavaPoet-based spec of a generated Javadoc text.
    JavaPoetName
    A value holder of JavaPoet TypeName.
    NestedClassName
    A name of a potentially nested class with outer class names separated with dots.
    TypeSpecWriter
    Writes the GeneratedTypeSpec to a file.
    UuidMethodFactory
    A MethodFactory used by default to create new static helper methods for UuidValue messages.

Package io.spine.code.gen.java Description

This package contains tools for generating Java code as well as working with already generated code.
